body.raw: The Tyringham Initiative (TI) was launched at Tyringham Hall in 2015, as a world-class think-tank for the evolution, expansion and deeper understanding of ‘new-paradigm consciousness’, renowned in its enquiry for exploration, innovation, rigour and integrity.
